
Build Odoo Module package
-------------------------
Usage:
    build_module <command>

Commands:
- Before setting up
    setup                               Setting up the package (addons path, language).

- After setting up
    update [argument]                   Update configuration of the package.
                                            [argument (optionnable): "addons_path", "language"]
    remove                              Delete configuration of the package.
    create [argument1] [argument1]      Create odoo module or models.
                                            [argument1 (optionnable): "module", "model", "model_inherited"]
                                            [argument2 (optionnable): module name]
    help                                Show help for commands.